	* modules/time.c (ctime): Pass correctly typed variable to
	m4_numeric_arg.
	(gmtime): Likewise.
	(localtime): Likewise.
	(strftime): Likewise.
	* m4/utility.c (m4_numeric_arg): For now, document arbitrary
	limit inherent in this interface.

