	* modules/m4.c (WEXITSTATUS): Provide fallback definition.
	(sysval): Use WEXITSTATUS.
	* modules/gnu.c (esyscmd): Set sysval to 0xffff, to accomodate both
	big-endian and little-endian wait status definitions.

