	* gnulib/import: Now updates makefile fragments, and configure.ac.
	* gnulib/m4/gnulib.am: New file.  Generated makefile fragments.
	* gnulib/m4/Makefile.am: include it.
	* gnulib/acm4/intmax.m4, gnulib/acm4/longdouble.m4,
