	(m4_symbol_delete):
	Use assert for internal errors.
	* m4/utility.c (m4_bad_argc, m4_numeric_arg, m4_dump_symbols): Use
	M4WARN.
	* modules/m4.c (undefine, defn, traceon, traceoff, dumpdef): use
	M4WARN and assert.
	* tests/builtins.at (pushpop): Adjust.

